main event: A UFO sighting was reported by the CAA Tower in Rosedale, California on November 10, 1954.
interesting points: The observation was made at 1925 PST,The object was noted to travel at a very high speed and at a low altitude,The color of the object was not specified,There is a possibility that some information was redacted in the document,The report refers to the use of Air Force Form 329.
